 will I be alerted before a deadline?",{"className":"group rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 open:shadow-sm","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 marker:content-none","children":["How quickly will I be alerted before a deadline?",["$","span",null,{"className":"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform","children":"▾"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed","children":"You receive your first alert 60 days before a deadline, a follow-up at 30 days, an urgent notice at 14 days, and a final warning at 7 days. Each alert is sent by email and, if configured, via Zapier to your preferred channel."}]]}],["$","details","What happens if my billing lapses?",{"className":"group rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 open:shadow-sm","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 marker:content-none","children":["What happens if my billing lapses?",["$","span",null,{"className":"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform","children":"▾"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed","children":"Your monitoring is paused and outbound alerts are suspended until payment resumes. No data is deleted — when payment is restored your monitoring automatically reactivates from where it left off."}]]}],["$","details","Can I monitor multiple companies?",{"className":"group rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 open:shadow-sm","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 marker:content-none","children":["Can I monitor multiple companies?",["$","span",null,{"className":"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform","children":"▾"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed","children":"Yes. Each company is monitored under a separate subscription. You can add companies from the dashboard at any time, and each gets its own independent deadline tracking and alert schedule."}]]}],["$","details","How is my company number verified?",{"className":"group rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 open:shadow-sm","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 marker:content-none","children":["How is my company number verified?",["$","span",null,{"className":"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform","children":"▾"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed","children":"We validate your company number against the Companies House API in real time at checkout and whenever we fetch deadline data. Only live, registered UK companies can be activated for monitoring."}]]}],["$","details","Is my payment data secure?",{"className":"group rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 open:shadow-sm","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 marker:content-none","children":["Is my payment data secure?",["$","span",null,{"className":"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform","children":"▾"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed","children":"All payments are processed by Stripe — we never store your card details. Our servers receive only tokenised subscription references. Stripe is PCI DSS Level 1 certified."}]]}],["$","details","Can I cancel at any time?",{"className":"group rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 open:shadow-sm","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 marker:content-none","children":["Can I cancel at any time?",["$","span",null,{"className":"ml-4 